<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10150122>
    dc:description "FIGURES 6–9. Hirmoneuropsis brevirostrata (Bigot, 1857): (6) dorsal view (photo by Pablo Núñez) and (7) male and female copulating (photo by Javier Gross); Hirmoneuropsis luctuosa (Philippi, 1865): (8) preyed by Araiopogon gayi (photo by Tomás Poch); Hirmoneuropsis orellanae (Stuardo, 1936): (9) dorsal view (photo by Patrick Vyvyan)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10150122/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10150124>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Distribution map of Hirmoneuropsis brevirostrata (Bigot, 1857) (green circles), H. luctuosa (Philippi, 1865) (red circles), and H. orellanai (Stuardo, 1936) (orange circles)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10150124/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

